  plantName: Aster Flower
  description: Asters symbolize love, wisdom, patience, and faith, often representing
    enchanted or refined love due to their star-shaped, daisy-like appearance. Known
    as the September birth flower and the 20th wedding anniversary flower, they commonly
    denote deep admiration and trust, historically associated with divine, magical,
    or protective properties.
